name: Oh No, Not My 3310!
description:
This is my submission for the "Mini Jame Gam #10" - The theme is "Reality is Breaking" and the special Object was a "Telephone".

Description

You play as NokiaMan, trying to escape the breaking of his reality, don't let the darkness catch you! 

Points

You gain points for every second you are alive, the higher on the screen you are the more points you get.

Controls

Movement - Left / Right

Jump - Space

Wall Jump - Jump away from wall while wall sliding

Oh No, Not My 3310! - v1.0 - PixGamesStudio 2022
